document_data.History:
During the [[Time of Troubles]] in [[1358 DR]], he met the then-mortal [[Kelemvor]], [[Midnight]], [[Cyric]], and the ex-cleric [[Adon]] when they arrived in the dale to seek advice from [[Elminster]]. Later, Rhaymon intended to fight against the armies of [[Bane]] in the [[second battle of Shadowdale]].

After the battle, however, when all believed Elminster dead, Rhaymon came to believe that Adon and Midnight were the culprits and testified against them in the process.{{cite book/Tantras|19-21|1}}

Some time later, Rhaymon died from an accident. Midnight met his spirit on the [[Fugue Plane]] and he gave some advice to her about [[Myrkul]]'s realm.{{cite book/Waterdeep|249-253|14}}
